<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Franz Pfinzing</head><p>Der Rat befiehlt Franz Pfinzing, Bürger zu Nürnberg, nach dem Ende der Messe unverzügliche Rückkehr nach Nürnberg und Vorsprache.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_189" id="93r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_189_r3l7"><expan>Francʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Pfincʒing <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_189_r3l8">Lıeber Francʒ / . Wir heiſʒen dich / VVenn du yecʒunden aws <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> meſʒe vertig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l9">werdeſt / daʒ du dann nyndert anderſwohin cʒieheſt / ſunder cʒeſtünde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l10">her heim gen Nüremberg cʒü vns kumſt / . vnd das <expan>gepiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir dir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l11">auch bey <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> eıde als du vns geſworen haſt / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r3l12"><expan>D<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> Letare / ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_189" id="93r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Francze<ex>n</ex></expan> Pfinczing <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Francz, wir heiszen dich, wenn du yeczunden aws
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> mesze vertig werdest, daz du dann nyndert
                        anderswohin cziehest, sunder czestünde her heim gen Nüremberg czü uns kumst.
                        Und das <expan>gepiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dir auch bey
                                <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> eide, als du uns gesworen hast.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> letare ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
